WEBVTT

NOTE: Estimated from known TTS script; timing requires human review before Tier 1 captions.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.827
If you need to sell your house fast in Akron, Ohio, USA Home Buyers gives you a direct cash-sale option without repairs, showings, or agent commissions.

2
00:00:10.827 --> 00:00:19.572
We buy Akron-area homes as-is throughout Summit County, including East Akron, Kenmore, Goodyear Heights, Highland Square, Firestone Park, and Northwest Akron.

3
00:00:19.572 --> 00:00:28.733
Maybe the property is older, inherited, vacant, tenant-occupied, behind on payments, or simply needs more repairs than you want to take on.

4
00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:33.730
A traditional buyer may want inspections, lender approval, and repairs before closing.

5
00:00:33.730 --> 00:00:37.478
We focus on making the sale clear and predictable.

6
00:00:37.478 --> 00:00:44.557
The process starts when you tell us about the house and what kind of timeline would help.

7
00:00:44.557 --> 00:00:49.970
We review the property, answer your questions, and make a written cash offer.

8
00:00:49.970 --> 00:00:53.718
If the offer works, you choose the closing date.

9
00:00:53.718 --> 00:00:59.131
You do not have to clean it out or make it market-ready first.

10
00:00:59.131 --> 00:01:02.046
There is no obligation and no pressure.

11
00:01:02.046 --> 00:01:09.958
We buy in the current condition and explain the offer so you understand the timing, costs, and next steps.

12
00:01:09.958 --> 00:01:18.287
If you want a straightforward cash offer for an Akron or Summit County home, call USA Home Buyers at 888-274-5006.

13
00:01:18.287 --> 00:01:23.700
We will help you decide if an as-is sale is the right move.
